channel.desc: Smut, smut and more smut - with sex and murder thrown in for good measure. Best friends Rita and Chris are a pair of homicide detectives who battle crime in the shadow of glitzy Palm Beach, Fla. As the series winds down, they are replaced by a former husband-and-wife team.
